<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
        <title>Projects · Jules ROY</title>
    </head>

    <body class="text-white bg-main-color font-Satoshi min-h-screen py-10 px-4 flex justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-6xl w-full">
            <div>
                <header class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 mb-10 pb-6 border-b border-border-color">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <a href="/" aria-label="Back to home">
                            <button class="custom-btn text-sm max-h-[40px] shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[3px] active:translate-y-[3px] text-gray-200 px-4 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded-lg flex items-center gap-2">
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4">
                                    <line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line>
                                    <polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Back to Home</span>
                            </button>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold font-CabinetGrotesk tracking-tight text-white">Projects</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm font-light text-gray-500 mt-1">A selection of my recent works and experiments</p>
                    </div>
                </header>

                <main class="grid gap-6 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">PixelMed</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Software</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">Cross-platform software for analyzing medical images (.png & .dcm) using image processing algorithms (CLAHE, Watershed, etc.).</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Python</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">PyQt6</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Oracle Cloud</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/pixelmed" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">PitLane Insider</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Web App</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">A platform that allows access to a wide variety of historical data concerning the Formula 1 world championship.</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">JS / Node.js</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">TailwindCSS</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Linux</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Data scraping</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/pitlaneinsider" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://pitlaneinsider.alwaysdata.net/" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs py-2 border border-border-color hover:border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-main-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">Try</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">FollowComp</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Chrome Extension</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">A Chrome extension that can be used to view the users you follow that don't follow you back.</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">JS</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Data scraping</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/followcomp" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/followcomp/dboemglicjcnfojjnijfaochbpopadjg" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs py-2 border border-border-color hover:border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-main-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">Try</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">VAL Project</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Simulation</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">This project is a simulation of the Lille metro, with C++ and the SFML library. Carried out in group as part of an end-of-semester project.</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">C++</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">CMake</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">SFML</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/projet_val" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">Dunetaler</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Game</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">A video game inspired by the game Undertale (by Toby Fox). Made in group as part of the project closing the year of CIR1 at ISEN Lille</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">PHP</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">JS</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">MySQL</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/Dunetaler" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://dunetaler.alwaysdata.net/php/inscription.php" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs py-2 border border-border-color hover:border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-main-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">Try</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card bg-second-color p-5 rounded-lg border border-border-color hover:border-third-color transition duration-75 ease-in-out flex flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">F1 Circuits SVG</h2>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-third-color bg-third-color/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-third-color/20 font-bold">Open Source</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-light">All Formula 1 circuit layouts and their evolutions from 1950 to nowadays. A project outside my usual area of ​​expertise, but one that allowed me to make my first foray into the world of open-source projects by contributing to the <a href="https://github.com/f1db/f1db" target="_blank" class="underline">f1db</a> repository.</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">SVG</span>
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-main-color border border-border-color px-2 py-0.5 rounded">GitHub</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="https://github.com/julesr0y/f1-circuits-svg" target="_blank" class="flex-1">
                                <button class="w-full text-xs shadow-custom shadow-third-color active:shadow-none active:translate-x-[2px] active:translate-y-[2px] text-gray-200 py-2 border border-third-color hover:text-third-color transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out bg-second-color cursor-pointer rounded flex items-center justify-center gap-2">GitHub</button>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
